<div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 columns">
        <h3>Skill Requirements</h3>

        <p>
            Our team is a competition-only cheerleading squad, meaning we specifically look for stunting, tumbling, and
            jumping ability.
        </p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="large-4 columns">
                <h4>Tumbling</h4>

                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Standing: </strong>Standing tuck. Jumps to tuck strongly encouraged
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Standing series: </strong>Two back handsprings ending in a tuck or better.
                             Jumps to standing series tumbling pass will also be evaluated
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Running: </strong>Round-off back handspring tuck
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="large-4 columns">
                <h4>Flyers</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Heel Stretch, Scorpion, Scale, Arabesque
                    </li>
                    <li>Full down from all stunts (double preferred)
                    </li>
                    <li>Basket experience preferred but not required
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="large-4 columns">
                <h4>Bases and Backs</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Solid group stunting for all body positions
                    </li>
                    <li>Clean catches of double downs
                    </li>
                    <li>Bases with the ability to Side and Main are preferred
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

